data.description: This stunning two story, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath with office/study, solar panels and water softener has it all! Nestled in the highly desired Vistas at Knox Ridge, this beauty offers modern & contemporary living at its finest. Conveniently located minutes away from 1604, this home is just a stone's throw away from Randolph AFB, entertainment, dining and shopping.
